    "en": {
      "title": "Day of Mourning for late Japanese PM",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ministry of Public Administration, Home Affairs said that Tuesday (12) shall be declared a day of Mourning by the Sri Lanka Government, due to the sudden passing of the former Japanese Prime Minister, the late Shinzo Abe.",
        "The Government informed to half-mast of the National Flag in all Government Institutions on Tuesday (12).",
        "Furthermore, it announced that Tuesday (12) NOT be a public holiday."
      ],
